|               |     TableScan: cpu, partial_filters=[cpu.usage_small = Int16(10) OR cpu.usage_small = Int16(20)]                                                  |
|               | ]]                                                                                                                                                |
| physical_plan | CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                   |
|               |   MergeScanExec: REDACTED
|               |                                                                                                                                                   |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

